text: Ngor is a monastery in the Ü-Tsang province of Tibet * Ngor, Dakar, a commune of Senegal * A Cambodian Hakka Romanization of the surname 吳, known as Ng or Wu * Ngor Royal Cup, lowest level of club football competition which competed in the tournament in Thailand since 1963 * Ngor Okpala, a Local Government Area of Imo State, Nigeria ==See also== * Ngo (disambiguation)
title: Ngor (disambiguation)
